snippet.textDisplay:
From India with ❤️A friend heard/saw this song recently and had this to say 👇🏻



Macha macha macha…

I’ve gone mentaaal with this song.

Last night, watched this video and many reaction videos at least 50 times! 

Hands down, the song of 2024 for me!! 
❤️‍🔥

Such beautiful harmony of multiple languages- Farsi, Persian, Balochi, Norwegian, English 

And the video is such a cool celebration of togetherness and happiness!

And to top it, there’s also some superb one-sided love expressed in the song and lyrics… pretty deep and soulful! 

10 on 10 song for me!!
